  <brief_title>Estimated Glomerular Filtration Rate After Kidney Transplantation - the Formula MDRD, CKD-EPI or Cockroft-Gault?</brief_title>
  <acronym>eGFR</acronym>
  <official_title>Estimated Glomerular Filtration Rate After Kidney Transplantation - the Formula Modification of Diet in Renal Disease (MDRD), Chronic Kidney Disease Epidemiology Collaboration (CKD-EPI) or Cockroft-Gault?</official_title>
  <sponsors>
