  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The study included 300 patients who are post-kidney transplantation (&gt; 3 months and &lt;10
      years). An analysis of body composition using bioelectrical impedance, calculated BMI and
      serum creatinine was determined. Glomerular filtration rate (GFR) was calculated using the
      formula CKD-EPI, Modification of Diet in Renal Disease (MDRD) and Cockroft-Gault.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
